    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，要等写数据完成。具体条件是WVALID、WREADY同时为高，而且WLAST为1，表示最后一个数据。这个转移可以标注为\"W complete\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITING",
        "IDLE",
        "WVALID && WREADY && WLAST"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2来画。起始点用[*]指向IDLE，然后IDLE到WRITING的转移加上AW handshake的标注，WRITING回IDLE加上W complete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "stateDiagram-v2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来结构是对的。不过转移条件里的逻辑表达式要清晰一点，AWVALID && AWREADY和WVALID && WREADY && WLAST都要保留，这是协议的关键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AWVALID && AWREADY",
        "WVALID && WREADY && WLAST"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
