      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，把逻辑表达式放在标注里用括号注明了。现在IDLE到WRITING的箭头写的是\"AW handshake (AWVALID && AWREADY)\"，返回那条是\"W complete (WVALID && WREADY && WLAST)\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
